var game={words:[{word:"copper"},{word:"explain"},{word:"fated"},{word:"truck"},{word:"neat"},{word:"unite"},{word:"branch"},{word:"educated"},{word:"tenuous"},{word:"hum"},{word:"decisive"},{word:"notice"}],wordToGuess:"",wordLength:"",guessProgress:[],guessedLetters:[],getRandomWord:function(){var e=Math.floor(Math.random()*this.words.length);return this.words[e]},initalizeGame:function(){this.wordToGuess=this.getRandomWord().word;for(var e=0;e<this.wordToGuess.length;e++)this.guessProgress.push("_");this.showGuessProgress()},showGuessProgress:function(){document.getElementById("word").innerHTML=this.guessProgress.join(" "),document.getElementById("guessedLetters").innerHTML=this.guessedLetters.join(" ")},isGuessed:function(e,s){return s.indexOf(e)!==-1},isLetter:function(e){return 1===e.length&&e.match(/[a-z]/i)},guess:function(e){this.key=String.fromCharCode(e.keyCode).toLowerCase(),this.isLetter(this.key)&&(this.isGuessed(this.key,this.guessedLetters)||(this.wordToGuess.indexOf(this.key)===-1?this.guessWrong():this.guessCorrect(),this.showGuessProgress()))},guessWrong:function(){this.guessedLetters.push(this.key),document.getElementById("guessesLeft").innerHTML--},guessCorrect:function(){for(var e=0;e<this.wordToGuess.length;e++)this.wordToGuess[e]===this.key&&(this.guessProgress[e]=this.key)}};window.onload=function(){game.initalizeGame()},document.onkeyup=function(e){game.guess(e)};